#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "The following global controls are available in the top panel of the screen.\n"
msgstr "螢幕頂部面板中提供了以下全域控制。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"preset\n"
": Select an existing module group preset.\n"
msgstr ""
"預置\n"
"：選擇現有的模組預置。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"remove\n"
": Remove the current preset (user-defined presets only).\n"
msgstr ""
"刪除\n"
"：刪除目前預置（僅限使用者定義的預置）。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"duplicate\n"
": Duplicate the current preset with a new name. The above example shows a new preset named \"user defined\", which has been created by duplicating the \"modules: default\" preset.\n"
msgstr ""
"複製\n"
"：用新名稱複製目前預置。 上面的示例顯示了一個名為“使用者定義”的新預置，透過複製“模組:預設”的預置創建的。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rename\n"
": Rename the current preset (user-defined presets only). Right-click to bring up a menu that can be used to copy, paste, select all, delete or insert an emoji).\n"
msgstr ""
"更名\n"
"：重命名目前預置（僅限使用者定義的預置）。 右鍵點擊彈出選單，可用於複製、貼上、全選、刪除或插入表情符號）。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"new\n"
": Create a new preset containing a minimal list of modules.\n"
msgstr ""
"新建\n"
"：創建一個包含最小模組列表的新預置。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"show search line\n"
": Choose whether to display the search bar below the module group icons\n"
msgstr ""
"顯示搜尋線\n"
"：選擇是否在模組分組圖示下方顯示搜尋欄\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"show quick access panel\n"
": Choose whether to display the quick access panel. If checked, a new entry will appear in the bottom panel to allow you to add or remove widgets.\n"
msgstr ""
"顯示快速訪問面板\n"
"：選擇是否顯示快速訪問面板。 如果是，新條目將出現在底部面板中，可增加或刪除小部件。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"show all history modules in active group\n"
": Select this to show all modules that are present in the [history stack](../pixelpipe/history-stack.md) within the active group, regardless of whether or not they are actually active.\n"
msgstr ""
"顯示啟用組中的所有歷史模組\n"
"：選擇此選項以顯示啟用組內 [歷史堆棧](../pixelpipe/history-stack.md) 中存在的所有模組，無論它們是否實際處於啟用狀態。"
"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"auto-apply this preset\n"
": Module group presets can be automatically applied based on the type of image being worked on. The check box indicates whether this preset currently has any auto-apply rules. Click on the gear icon to amend the auto-apply settings. See [presets](../processing-modules/presets.md) for details.\n"
msgstr ""
"自動套用此預置\n"
"：可以根據正在處理的影像類型自動套用模組分組預置。 該核取方塊指示此預置目前是否有任何自動套用規則。 點擊齒輪圖示以修改自動套用設定。 有關詳細信息，"
"請參閱 [預置](../processing-modules/presets.md)。\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#: content/darkroom/organization/module-groups.md
#: content/overview/workflow/process.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "module groups"
msgstr "模組分組"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "The bottom panel of the screen allows you to alter the quick access panel and module groups for the selected preset (user-defined presets only).\n"
msgstr "螢幕底部面板可更改選定的快速訪問面板和模組分組（僅限使用者自定的預置）。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"add a group\n"
": Click on the + sign beside the \"module groups\" label to add a new group. \n"
msgstr ""
"增加分組\n"
"：點擊“模組分組”標籤旁邊的 + 號以增加新分組。 \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"remove a group\n"
": Remove a group by clicking on the X button beside the group name.\n"
msgstr ""
"刪除分組\n"
"：通過點擊分組名稱旁邊的 X 按鈕可刪除分組。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"add a module/widget\n"
": Add a module to a group, or a widget to the quick access panel, by clicking the + sign below the group name. Select the required module/widget from the displayed list. \n"
msgstr ""
"增加模組/小工具\n"
"：通過點擊組名稱下方的 + 號，將模組增加到分組，或將小工具增加到快速訪問面板。 從顯示的列表中選擇所需的模組/小工具。 \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"remove a module/widget\n"
": Remove a module from a group, or a widget from the quick access panel, by clicking the X beside the module/widget name.\n"
msgstr ""
"刪除模組/小工具\n"
"：通過點擊模組/小工具名稱旁邊的 X，從組中刪除模組，或從快速訪問面板中刪除小工具。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"change a group's icon\n"
": Change the icon assigned to a group by clicking on the existing group icon and selecting a new one from the displayed list.\n"
msgstr ""
"更改分組的圖示\n"
"：點擊現有分組圖示並從顯示的列表中選擇一個新圖示來更改分配給分組的圖示。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"change the group order\n"
": Change the order in which the groups are displayed by clicking on the < and > buttons below the group names.\n"
msgstr ""
"更改分組順序\n"
"：點擊分組名稱下方的 < 及 > 按鈕變更分組的顯示順序。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/manage-module-layouts.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rename a group\n"
": Rename a module group by clicking on the group name and typing. Right-click to bring up a menu that can be used to copy, paste, select all, delete or insert an emoji)\n"
msgstr ""
"分組更名\n"
"：點擊分組名稱並鍵入以更名模組分組。 右鍵點擊帶出選單，可用於複製、貼上、全選、刪除或插入表情符號）\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/organization/module-groups.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "A number of pre-defined module groups are shipped with darktable and are selectable as presets. These are summarized below.\n"
