msgstr ""
"darktable 使用 Lua 5.4 版。 描述 Lua 的原理和語法超出了此使用手冊的範圍。 詳細介紹參閱[Lua參考手冊](http://www."
"lua.org/manual/5.4/manual.html)。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/lua/overview.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "The following sections will provide you with a brief introduction to how Lua scripts can be used within darktable.\n"
