msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/retouch.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"scales\n"
": Shows how many detail layers the image has been decomposed into. Zero indicates that no wavelet decomposition has been performed.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/retouch.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"current\n"
": Shows which layer is currently selected (also marked with the light gray dot on the bar graph).\n"
