#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/metadata-editor.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "When several images are selected having different values for a given metadata field, the module displays _<leave unchanged>_ for that field -- if you choose to apply changes, these fields will not be changed. If you right-click on the field the different values are listed at the end of the contextual menu. Select one of the values in the menu to apply that value to all of the selected images -- the change will be saved once you press the \"apply\" button or the Enter/Tab key.\n"
