msgid ""
"metadata entry fields\n"
": A separate field is displayed for each metadata item. Hold Ctrl while scrolling with your mouse to increase the height of a field. Press Ctrl+Enter to insert a new line. Double-click on a field's label to delete the contents of that field.\n"
