#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/collection-filters.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Within the extension field, you can also use the keywords `RAW` (to select all handled RAW file extensions), `NOT RAW` (to select all non-RAW file extensions), `LDR` (to select low-dynamic-range extensions) or `HDR` (to select high-dynamic-range extensions).\n"
